---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="about · wanderlust" description="About Ashi and wanderlust.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest" style="color: var(--color-muted)">
      about
    </p>
    <h1 class="font-display mt-4 text-4xl font-medium leading-[1.05] tracking-tight md:text-5xl">
      Hi, I'm Ashi.
    </h1>

    <div class="prose-trip mt-10">
      <p>
        Software engineer working remotely from India. 40+ countries in the
        last five years and counting. Friends kept asking for my itineraries,
        so I started writing them down properly. This site is the result.
      </p>

      <p>
        Each itinerary is what I actually did: day-by-day, with the bookings
        worth making ahead, the food worth chasing, and the days worth skipping.
        When a trip splits into two vibes (chill island vs party island, city
        day vs day trip), I keep both branches so you can pick.
      </p>

      <h3>Why free</h3>

      <p>
        Travel content behind paywalls or affiliate links has gotten weird.
        These itineraries are free, ad-free, and won't try to upsell you a
        course. If something here helped, share it with someone planning
        the same trip.
      </p>

      <h3>Find me elsewhere</h3>

      <p>
        Instagram: <a href="https://instagram.com/aaashi.b">@aaashi.b</a>.
        That's where I announce new trips and post the unserious stuff.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
